                    </article>

                                                                                                </div>
                        

                        <p>Swish.</p>
<p>Time expires. Detroit comes alive as it has not done since Henry Ford's time and the waiting fans storm the court to mob their local boys who just made good. All is right with the world, and another story only sports can bring us comes full circle.</p>
<p>If only the truth could have been this good.</p>
<p>Brett Aresco is a Trinity senior. His column runs every other Thursday.</p>
